{"id":88580,"type":4,"name":"Ultima Underworld: The Stygian Abyss","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/ae/6f/88580_javzK.jpg","summary":"Ultima Underworld: The Stygian Abyss is a first-person role-playing video game (RPG) developed by Blue Sky Productions (later Looking Glass Studios) and published by Origin Systems. Released in March 1992, the game is set in the fantasy world of the Ultima series. It takes place inside the Great Stygian Abyss: a large cave system that contains the remnants of a failed utopian civilization. The player assumes the role of the Avatar—the Ultima series' protagonist—and attempts to find and rescue a baron's kidnapped daughter. ","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>地下创世纪：冥河深渊</li><li><span>开发: </span>Blue Sky Productions (<a href=\"/person/39129\">Looking Glass Studios</a>)</li><li><span>发行: </span><a href=\"/person/40779\">Origin Systems</a>、<a href=\"/person/13930\">Electronic Arts</a></li><li><span>遊戲設計師: </span><a href=\"/person/40818\">Richard Garriott</a></li><li><span>制作人: </span><a href=\"/person/40713\">Warren Spector</a></li><li><span>平台: </span>PS</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>DOS</li><li><span>游玩人数: </span>1</li><li><span>发行日期: </span>1992年3月</li>","collection":{"collect":1},"tags":[{"name":"Ultima","count":1},{"name":"LookingGlassStudios","count":1},{"name":"OriginSystems","count":1},{"name":"ImmersiveSim","count":1},{"name":"CRPG","count":1},{"name":"WarrenSpector","count":1},{"name":"1992","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":39129,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/47/e5/39129_prsn_k8HXX.jpg","name":"Looking Glass Studios","desc":"开发"},{"id":13930,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/ed/80/13930_prsn_10ahO.jpg","name":"艺电","desc":"发行"},{"id":40779,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/6c/88/40779_prsn_ANIB7.jpg","name":"Origin Systems","desc":"发行"},{"id":40818,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/d2/0b/40818_prsn_v5noZ.jpg","name":"理查·盖瑞特","desc":"遊戲設計師"},{"id":40713,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/77/db/40713_prsn_58WCW.jpg","n